Class DimBlock

java.lang.Object
cst8221.assignment.component.DimBlock
public class DimBlock
extends java.lang.Object
Class Name: DimBlock Method List: DimBlock(), DimBlock(int dim), addButton(JButton button), ArrayList getButtons(), setButtons(ArrayList buttons) Constant List: Purpose: The class DimBlock is used to group the blocks of buttons that belong to the same dimension (e.g. dim=2, buttons at row 0, 1 and col 0, 1 will be grouped) with respect to Sudoku game logic.
